                    We have the best books in the world. You will love reading them.
                    We have a large selection of books from different categories.
                    You will definitely find what makes you happy.
                </p>
                <br />
                <form class="d-flex" action="/Books">
                    <input class="form-control me-2" name="search" placeholder="Search by Title or Author">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-light" type="submit">Search</button>
                </form>

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="/images/books.png" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

